</code></pre> <p>The concept is to pass the necessary information as a hash (in Perl) or dictionary (in Python).</p> PerlPython <pre><code>$bff = {
    data =&gt; $my_bff_json_data,
    method =&gt; 'bff2pxf'
};
</code></pre> <pre><code>bff = {
     "data" : my_bff_json_data,
     "method" : "bff2pxf"
}
</code></pre> <p>The data will be sent as <code>POST</code> to the API's URL (see more info here). <pre><code>{
"data": {...}
